      <title>基辅遭乌克兰全境导弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/kyiv-comes-under-attack-in-missile-strike-across-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰首都周一遭到袭击，这是该国全国性袭击的一部分，据乌克兰空军报告，俄罗斯部署了“匕首”导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/kyiv-comes-under-attack-in-missile-strike-across-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:54:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈贝克称，法国考试成绩令人鼓舞但也充满挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-result-encouraging-but-represents-challenge-habeck-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国经济部长罗伯特哈贝克表示，法国议会提前投票的结果令人欣慰，但其影响可能会考验国内政治和更广泛的地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-result-encouraging-but-represents-challenge-habeck-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:45:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举结果公布后逢低买入者涌现，法国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市上涨，扭转了早盘的跌势，因为在左翼政党意外获胜、议会出现分裂且没有明显多数的情况下，投资者将选举结果视为“最不坏”的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国避免极右翼获胜但马克龙无人执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/france-dodges-far-right-win-but-macron-has-no-one-who-can-govern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 领导的极右翼政党在周日的选举中惨败，导致法国议会出现分裂，没有明显多数，法国正陷入长期的政治僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/france-dodges-far-right-win-but-macron-has-no-one-who-can-govern</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
