    <item>
      <title>英国工党总理里夫斯将在首次演讲中公布工党的增长计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/uk-s-reeves-to-unveil-labour-s-growth-plan-in-first-major-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 将于周一在担任财政大臣后的首次重要演讲中阐述新工党政府刺激私人投资的计划，该党试图借助上周在英国大选中的压倒性胜利来推动经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/uk-s-reeves-to-unveil-labour-s-growth-plan-in-first-major-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
